### ==============================================
### 🔥 FINTRACK API TEST SUITE (PHASE 1)
### Harap gunakan ekstensi "REST Client" di VS Code 
### untuk mempermudah. Klik tulisan "Send Request"
### ==============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
# Ganti accessToken dengan token dari respons Login
@accessToken = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
# Token dari Category setelah create
@categoryId = YOUR_CATEGORY_ID_HERE
# Token dari Account setelah create
@accountId = YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID_HERE

### ---------------- HEALTH CHECK ----------------

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### ---------------- 1. AUTH MODULE ----------------

### 1.1 Register
# @name registerUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Budi Santoso",
  "email": "budi@fintrack.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 1.2 Login (Lakukan ini untuk mendapat Token!)
# @name loginUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "budi@fintrack.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 1.3 Get Profile / Me
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ---------------- 2. CATEGORY MODULE ----------------
# Jangan lupa ganti @accessToken di atas dengan token hasil Login!

### 2.1 Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2.2 Create Custom Category
# @name createCategory
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kopi Susu",
  "type": "expense",
  "icon": "☕",
  "color": "#8B5A2B"
}

### 2.3 Update Custom Category
# Ganti dengan ID Category yang baru dibuat
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kopi Kekinian"
}

### 2.4 Delete Custom Category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ---------------- 3. ACCOUNT MODULE ----------------

### 3.1 Get All Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3.2 Create Account
# @name createAccount
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "BCA Utama",
  "type": "bank",
  "initialBalance": 5000000,
  "icon": "🏦",
  "color": "#1E3A8A"
}

### 3.3 Get Account By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3.4 Update Account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "BCA Tabungan",
  "icon": "💸"
}

### 3.5 Archive (Soft Delete) Account
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
